Glintung Go Green (Kampung 3G) is a world-class, community-based environmental movement that transformed a flood-prone slum in Malang into an internationally recognised model for urban sustainability. Led by Kalpataru Award-winning visionary **Ir. H. Bambang Irianto**, the platform serves as the digital gateway for their eco-tourism programme and environmental consultancy services.

---

## Key Features

- **Impact-Driven Storytelling** — A comprehensive landing page communicating a 10-year transformation journey — from urban slum to global sustainability model — using data-driven *before vs. after* comparisons.
- **Programme Portfolio** — Detailed modules for six core initiatives, including the flagship **GEMAR** (Water Saving Movement) featuring large-scale biopore and injection well installations, and a Waste Bank system.
- **Recognition & Award Showcase** — A dedicated gallery and timeline for national and international accolades, including the **Kalpataru Award** and the **Guangzhou International Award for Urban Innovation** (Top 15 out of 301 cities worldwide).
- **Edu-Tourism Management** — Integrated contact and inquiry systems for visitors from all 34 Indonesian provinces and international delegations who study the village's sustainable urban farming and waste management models.
- **Institutional Credibility Design** — A clean, nature-inspired UI that balances the grassroots village identity with the professional credibility required to engage ministries, universities, and global organisations.

---

## Tech Stack

Built with **Next.js**, delivering a high-performance, SEO-optimised platform for a globally recognised environmental initiative.

---

## Our Contribution

> *"The challenge was representing a decade of grassroots community work in a way that resonates with both local residents and international environmental agencies. Every design decision had to serve both audiences simultaneously."*

This project demonstrates **Ariverse Studio's** ability to handle high-profile institutional branding — translating social impact into a professional digital presence with real global reach.
